# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ISE ACME Manager — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values you need.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Custom DNS Server (optional)
# Sets the DNS server used globally by ALL processes inside the daemon container
# (overrides /etc/resolv.conf via Docker's dns: directive in docker-compose.yml).
# Steps:
#   1. Uncomment the line below and set your DNS server IP.
#   2. Uncomment the `dns:` line in docker-compose.yml under the `daemon` service.
#   3. Restart the container: docker compose down && docker compose up -d
# Leave commented out to use Docker's default DNS.
# CUSTOM_DNS_SERVER=192.168.1.53
